    <body>When you are working in the XML Editor, you can use the F4 or CTRL+Y shortcuts to repeat your last action. This feature uses the same controller that is used when you create macros in Flare<MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="General.OnlineLive,Snippets.Snippet2"> (see <MadCap:xref href="../../../Macros/About_Macros.htm">About Macros</MadCap:xref>)</MadCap:conditionalText>. Therefore, only actions that are supported by the macro controller are supported for these <MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Snippets.Snippet2">new </MadCap:conditionalText>repeat shortcuts.</body>
</html>